@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED

      Gewei,
      Volum,
      Voleh,
      Descr,
      Bldat,
      Extco,
      Desco,
      Extrg,
      Desrg,
      Pymty,
      PaymentTermsName,
      Trnty,
      Cuscd,

      Cofrp,
      Shpfr,
      Sfrrp,
      Brofr,

      Reffn,
      Bankl,
      BankID,
      BankCountry,
      BankWaers,
      Iban,
      IsAccounting,
      Eori,
      ContractNo,
      Beyam,
      _InvoiceHeader   : redirected to composition child ZETR_DDL_C_EXP_INVH,
      _InvoiceItem     : redirected to composition child ZETR_DDL_C_EXP_INVI,
      _Texts           : redirected to composition child ZETR_DDL_C_EXP_TXT,
      _BillingDocument : redirected to composition child ZETR_DDL_C_BIL_DOC,
      _Costing         : redirected to composition child ZETR_DDL_C_COSTING_RPR
